I finally found a way to keep the thumbnails from getting corrupted when device maintenance wants to optimize. Disable the app in settings. Do not default to factory default, hit cancel. Run device maintenance. Now re-enable the app. You have to put the shortcut back on the homescreen. Permissions gets turned off. Turn storage permission back on. Launch Drive. All of the saved data will be intact including thumbs. Drive needs to get protected in an update to prevent the cache from being cleared.
